{
  "stem": "12255.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were told they're being taken to a very nice camp where there'd be only Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So with great difficulty, we loaded these people onto the trucks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we started off early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was driving-- I was not driving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was sitting in the cab of one of the things, and the other two in other cabs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we started.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, it was a long, long distance, a long distance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It-- altogether it took us about 10 hours to get from Bergen-Belsen to this camp which was called Diepholz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not too far from a place called Osnabruck in northern Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a terrible journey because the roads were very bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'd been blown up and blasted and so on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there were many times where we had to take too long detours through fields and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the people were not in the best of health for a job like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, and, of course, from time to time, they had to stop to allow people to carry out their natural functions and so on, which they had to do in the fields, and-- And I'll never forget one little incident, which I think I must speak about.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We stopped at a little hamlet, what one might call it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the people got off the, the lorries.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And just nearby was a little market garden kind of place, you know, a big garden with chickens running around and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, they just ran into these little farms and started pulling out the vegetables and grabbing the chickens and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The officer in command of the whole expedition was a lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he tried to create order.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
